COMMENT ON COLUMN steps.procedure_version IS 'Procedure version containing the step; maps to pko:hasStep/pplan:isStepOfPlan.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN steps.step_number IS 'Stable sequence label; maps to pko:stepNumber.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN steps.title IS 'Human-readable step title.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN steps.step_kind IS 'Atomic or MultiStep.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN steps.assigned_role IS 'Role responsible for the step.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN steps.instruction IS 'Normative step instruction.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN steps.expected_duration_minutes IS 'Expected duration represented as an OWL-Time duration in semantic projections.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN steps.expertise_level IS 'PKO expertise level: Junior, Senior, Expert, or Master.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN steps.requires_human_confirmation IS 'TRUE when a human must confirm the step; maps to pko:wasConfirmedBy at execution.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN steps.control_kind IS 'What kind of control this step is: Preparation, Approval, LegalReview, Verification, Extraction, Publication, Retrospective, or None. That policy-04 is a legal review is a property OF policy-04, not of a formula that happens to name it; storing it as data makes downstream predicates portable to procedures that do not exist yet.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN steps.semantic_type_iri IS 'Exact P-Plan class IRI.';

